value: Andes of c Argentina to Tierra del Fuego and Falkland Islands

Temperate zone of southern South America, from north-central Chile (Atacama) and Argentina (San Juan, Santa Fe) south to Tierra del Fuego; Falkland Islands. Sea level to 2,800 meters. Migratory in southern part of range.
